Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手一搏吧「Wake Up. Girls!」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照着平常做的去发挥就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请从那边下台
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I-1 club要上台了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.16,0:02:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么偏偏在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.49,0:02:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏是这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.56,0:02:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳佳 在里面么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快到集合时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上过去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？怎么了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.37,0:02:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给自己鼓了鼓劲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳佳 马上就要彩排了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.13,0:02:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是一组只有十分钟的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.89,0:02:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.22,0:02:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圆阵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.28,0:02:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好干啊队长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向前走！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.21,0:02:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加个油！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wake up, Girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放音乐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳佳 那里不是0号位哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.67,0:03:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个center在干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作整个慢半拍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳佳 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的脚有点不对劲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道刚才摔倒的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.27,0:03:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:51.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧 没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.99,0:03:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看上去就很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:57.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳佳 还是别太勉强了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.72,0:03:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再恶化了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要坚持五分钟就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.64,0:04:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以坚持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我不想放弃 绝对不想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.94,0:04:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家别管我了 请上台去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果没有center的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在再换编排也来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.05,0:04:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弃权吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不行 不能弃权
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.47,0:04:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.72,0:04:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你们了 快去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.67,0:04:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 弃权吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许没有佳佳 剩下的人硬上也能行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但没有你的舞台 是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.10,0:05:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真梦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.35,0:05:06.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不在的话 我认为没有意义
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七个人一起才是「Wake Up. Girls!」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 真的 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.42,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么办 社长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.82,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是老样子在玩过家家？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真梦和从前完全没变呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在外面偷听么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是恶趣味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志保 对不起 我们今天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.34,0:05:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你们弃权的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些包扎只能维持之后的几个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演出结束了记得好好去医院治疗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.30,0:06:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.86,0:06:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志保
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是个好人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.45,0:06:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能因为这而掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:38.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳佳 绸带里面没有藏着图钉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说那个也是足尖鞋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 感觉好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.25,0:06:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了万无一失还是变更一下编排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.19,0:06:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是尽量减轻风险吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.96,0:06:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的副歌那里的跳跃 我觉得改一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:02.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起大家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.47,0:07:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要那么用力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.59,0:07:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扯断了可不是个好兆头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 不是说手环带到断的时候愿望就能实现么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.19,0:07:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意说是手环更像木屐的带子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.89,0:07:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.73,0:07:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打起精神来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.21,0:07:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.88,0:07:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那这个部分 我就来代替佳佳做这个动作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我这样过来 做这个动作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.90,0:07:42.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要自然到让大家觉得这就是原来的编排哟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳佳觉得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“七个人一起才是「Wake Up. Girls!」”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些成员之中 每个人都是无可替代的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七个人在一起才能成为「Wake Up. Girls!」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.47,0:08:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.39,0:08:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大致算是成型了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 差不多该上台了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有五分钟演出就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.55,0:09:11.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请还在大厅里的观众回到各自的座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.90,0:09:14.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.86,0:09:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎各位来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是I-1 club总经理 白木
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「偶像祭典」总决赛 终于要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:47.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天在这里I-1竞技场
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了I-1 club的公认对手的称号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过日本全国激烈的选赛的角逐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.83,0:09:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有六支组合来到了这里进行最后的对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:10:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娱乐 到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶像 到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我自己的心中有一个答案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.42,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这与2001年9月11日在纽约发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.12,0:10:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那起悲惨的事件有关
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当日 在百老汇正有一出新剧预定上演
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:20.63,up-left,NTP,30,0,30,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fs45}注：预定于2001年9月11日在百老汇上演的音乐剧「妈妈咪呀！」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:26.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 事件发生后的纽约沉浸在悲痛中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.03,0:10:26.47,up-left,NTP,30,0,30,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fs45}不幸恰逢9·11恐怖袭击事件发生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当天那部作品也不得不中止上演
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.78,0:10:30.05,up-left,NTP,30,0,30,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fs45}同期剧目都因为此而不得不停演一周
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:34.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那部作品的作者感觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对深受伤害的纽约市民来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.00,0:10:36.29,up-left,NTP,30,0,30,,{\c&HFFFFFF&\fs45}只有「妈妈咪呀！」在9月12日晚依旧开演并观众满席
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这正是娱乐应该带来的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.52,0:10:43.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是毫不迟疑的重开了剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:43.17,up-left,NTP,30,0,30,,{\fs45\c&HFFFFFF&}之后该剧被誉为“拯救‘9·11’的百老汇奇迹”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.92,0:10:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9·11啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:51.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得 这才是娱乐的真谛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:56.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而偶像也正是其中的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.07,0:11:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天出场的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是在这娱乐世界的角落里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们朝着顶点而努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:08.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里争锋相对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.97,0:11:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请在座的各位不要吝惜自己的掌声和欢呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为出场的所有人送上你们的应援
